<p><strong>Over-by-over report:</strong> England batted (slowly), wickets fell (occasionally), and the home side edged towards a 3-0 end-of-series final scoreline</p><div class="author"><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/profile/simonburnton">Simon Burnton</a></div><div class="author"><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/profile/johnashdown">John Ashdown</a></div><br/><p style="clear:both" /><img width='1' height='1' src='http://feeds.theguardian.com/c/34708/f/663870/s/304cf13c/sc/13/mf.gif' border='0'/><br clear='all'/><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/1/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/1/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/2/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/2/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/3/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/sc/13/rc/3/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/a2.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/a2.img" border="0"/></a><img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/173608247966/u/53/f/663870/c/34708/s/304cf13c/a2t.img" border="0"/>
